com.hp.mss.hpprint.model

Class PrintJobData

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hp.mss.hpprint.model.PrintJobData

  • public class PrintJobData
extends java.lang.Object
    PrintJobData is required for using the HP Print SDK workflow. It contains all the relevant info needed to build the print job.

      • getPrintItem

        public PrintItem getPrintItem(PrintAttributes.MediaSize mediaSize)
        This method gets a print item using a media size as the key. If the print item does not exist, the default print item will be used.
        Parameters:
        mediaSize - The media size of the print item you want to retrieve.
        Returns:
